\
## Recommended Tech Stack\
\
| Layer | Technology | Reason |\
|---|---|---|\
| Frontend + API | Next.js 14 (App Router) | React-based, API routes built in, Vercel-native |\
| Database + Auth | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | Auth, REST, realtime, row-level security, generous free tier |\
| UI Components | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | Fast to build, accessible, professional |\
| Email | Resend | Simple API, good deliverability, free tier |\
| CSV Parsing | Papa Parse | Client-side CSV parsing, no server load |\
| Hosting | Vercel | One-click Next.js deploy, free tier sufficient for MVP |\
| Domain | schools.ifoundit.io | Separate subdomain from main Wix site |\
