## Epic 1 \'97 School Admin Portal\
\
### Overview\
A password-protected web dashboard where a school administrator manages their students and tags. iFoundIt creates the school account and sends an invite email. The admin then logs in, imports students, and assigns tags.\
\
### Pages\
\
**`/login`**\
- Email + password login form\
- Uses Supabase Auth `signInWithPassword`\
- On success: redirect to `/dashboard`\
- "Forgot password" link (Supabase handles reset email)\
\
**`/dashboard`**\
- Summary cards: Total Tags, Active Tags, Unassigned Tags, Recoveries This Term\
- Recent found events table (last 5): date, student name (masked: "J. Smith"), resolved status\
- Quick action buttons: Import Students, Assign Tags, View All Events\
\
**`/students`**\
- Table: first name, last name, year group, form group, tag assigned (yes/no), active\
- Search/filter by year group and form\
- "Import CSV" button \uc0\u8594  opens CSV upload modal\
- "Add student manually" button \uc0\u8594  inline form\
- Row action: deactivate student (marks active = false, unlinks tag)\
\
**`/tags`**\
- Table: serial number, assigned to (student name or "Unassigned"), active status, last scanned date\
- "Assign Tag" action per row: dropdown to select student from list\
- "Bulk Assign" button: CSV upload mapping serial numbers to student names\
- Filter: unassigned only\
\
**`/events`**\
- Table: date/time, tag serial, student name, finder message, location, resolved (yes/no)\
- "Mark Resolved" toggle per row (updates `resolved_at`)\
- Date range filter\
\
**`/settings`**\
- School name, address (read-only, set by iFoundIt superadmin)\
- Notification email: editable, saved to `organisations.contact_email`\
- Notification phone: optional\
- Upload school logo (stored in Supabase Storage, used on finder page)\
\
### Superadmin Pages (role: `ifoundit_superadmin`)\
\
**`/admin`**\
- List of all organisations with tag counts and event counts\
- "Create School" button \uc0\u8594  form: name, slug, contact email, contact phone\
\
**`/admin/tags`**\
- "Provision Tags" form: paste or upload list of serial numbers, assign to organisation\
- Sets `organisation_id` and `active = true` on each tag record\
\
### Acceptance Criteria\
- [ ] School admin can log in and is redirected to their organisation's dashboard only\
- [ ] School admin cannot access another school's data (RLS enforced)\
- [ ] Dashboard summary cards show accurate counts\
- [ ] Superadmin can create a school account and provision tags in under 5 minutes\
\
